<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8166704>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Tigridia azufresensis. A. Habitat. B. Flowering plant. C. Plant with fruits. D. Flower in frontal view. E. Flower in lateral view with cauline leaf and spathe bracts. White arrows= basal leaf, red arrows = cauline leaf." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8166704/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8166706>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Tigridia azufresensis. A–B. Habit. C. Dissected flower (inner tepal sections: 1 = claw, 2 = blade, 3 = limb, 2 + 3 = lamina). D–E. Flower in frontal and lateral views. F. Style and stamens. G. Seeds. Illustrated by Ericka Belén Cortez Castro based on type material (G. Munguía-Lino et al. 921)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8166706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8166708>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution map of endemic species of Tigridia in the Transmexican Volcanic Belt. Biogeographical limit (black line), state limit (thick grey line)." ;
